casebody.data:
Mahoning County Bar Association v. Boano.

[Cite as Mahoning Cty. Bar Assn. v. Boano (1989), 46 Ohio St. 3d 146.]-

(No. 89-1096 — Submitted August 15, 1989 — Decided October 25, 1989.) David R. White and Stuart J. Banks, for relator. Charles W. Kettlewell, for respondent. Per Curiam.

We agree that respondent violated DR 1-102(A)(5) and also adopt the board’s recommendations. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimanded. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
